  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Overload your omni-tool's acetylene torch, spewing flames in front of you. Each creature within an 8m cone is primed (fire) until the start of your next turn and must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 6d10 fire damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>At the start of your turn, you may spend your action and 1 additional tech point to continue casting this power. Your movement speed is 2m while casting it in this manner. The spell ends if you become incapacitated.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>At Higher Levels: When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the damage increases by 2d10 for each slot level above 3rd.</p>",
